Maybe you're in need of wisdom today.

00:00:35.168 --> 00:00:37.312
You're facing a great decision.

00:00:38.464 --> 00:00:39.680
I don't know.

00:00:39.776 --> 00:00:45.792
Maybe there's somebody here today that just you love this music, but you don't know what it's about.

00:00:48.224 --> 00:00:51.584
You can resonate with these beautiful tunes and.

00:00:52.928 --> 00:00:55.296
The incredible voice.

00:00:56.736 --> 00:00:59.392
