In the quietness of this moment,

00:01:15.008 --> 00:01:19.680
I'd like for you to just pray for the person you're standing next to.

00:01:21.312 --> 00:01:23.840
You say, well, I don't know their name. That's okay

00:01:24.320 --> 00:01:25.792
God does.

00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:29.120
And there might be a burden that they're facing.

00:01:29.088 --> 00:01:30.848
A trouble, a problem,

00:01:30.880 --> 00:01:32.768
