00:01:34.144 --> 00:01:37.088
You don't know anything about it. God does.

00:01:38.944 --> 00:01:42.080
So the words to the song, can I pray for you?

00:01:43.744 --> 00:01:46.144
For this moment right here let's

00:01:46.336 --> 00:01:48.224
Just pray for one another.

00:01:48.928 --> 00:01:50.368
And say god

00:01:50.496 --> 00:01:52.096
I don't know the need.

00:01:52.480 --> 00:01:53.664
What you do?

00:01:53.952 --> 00:01:56.288
And right now the name of Jesus.

00:01:56.768 --> 00:02:00.064
I'm praying for this person I'm standing next to

00:02:00.544 --> 00:02:03.296
I'm praying for these people on my people

00:02:04.864 --> 00:02:11.392
Maybe God is bringing something to your mind. Maybe somebody's sitting behind you, sitting in front of you. You know.

00:02:11.488 --> 00:02:13.504
There's some kind of thing.

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:15.616
For God.

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:19.232
They're depending on him to show up in a mighty way.

00:02:21.888 --> 00:02:25.792
I'm going to lead us on a prayer this morning and if that's the case

00:02:26.592 --> 00:02:28.768
You need prayer today.

00:02:29.152 --> 00:02:30.944
I invite you to come.

00:02:32.096 --> 00:02:36.192
But in this moment, if you don't know Jesus as your Savior, friend,

00:02:36.032 --> 00:02:39.776
Why on earth would you leave this church house like that today?

00:02:42.528 --> 00:02:45.856
There's people around you that's praying for you right now.

00:02:48.256 --> 00:02:50.368
Don't leave here without the Lord.

00:02:52.320 --> 00:02:53.824
Trust in Moses.

00:02:53.952 --> 00:02:56.224
Word gives us admonition.

00:02:56.896 --> 00:03:00.224
If we can come boldly to the throne, we can ask God.

00:03:00.544 --> 00:03:03.104
For him to be our personal savior,

00:03:04.448 --> 00:03:05.984
From whosoever

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:08.256
Shall call upon the name of the Lord.

00:03:08.768 --> 00:03:10.144
Shall be saved.

00:03:11.872 --> 00:03:14.528
Father, in the quietness of this moment,

00:03:15.808 --> 00:03:18.176
We stand in this church house.

00:03:18.592 --> 00:03:20.832
And we have enjoyed this music.

00:03:21.056 --> 00:03:24.256
Who have enjoyed your servant that has come to share?

00:03:24.928 --> 00:03:27.712
For the beautiful music that has accompanied it.

00:03:30.624 --> 00:03:33.280
But now we focus on that one that's.

00:03:33.632 --> 00:03:37.152
Either behind us or in front of us or beside us.

00:03:37.312 --> 00:03:38.976
That's going through.

00:03:38.816 --> 00:03:40.576
A need of some sort.

00:03:43.200 --> 00:03:45.504
We don't know what that may be.

00:03:46.368 --> 00:03:49.952
But you have already seen it before we come to you today.

00:03:50.816 --> 00:03:53.280
And we pray right now in Jesus' name.

00:03:54.400 --> 00:03:58.016
And whatever it is that our brother our sister

00:03:58.496 --> 00:04:01.632
Needs the most in their heart and their life today.

00:04:03.040 --> 00:04:06.240
Maybe it's a physical need, a spiritual need.

00:04:06.368 --> 00:04:08.128
A financial need

00:04:08.160 --> 00:04:09.888
An emotional need.

00:04:10.912 --> 00:04:12.928
I don't know God, but you do.

00:04:14.592 --> 00:04:15.904
And I pray.

00:04:17.792 --> 00:04:19.488
In Jesus name

00:04:20.736 --> 00:04:24.096
That you would do something far beyond incredible.

00:04:25.856 --> 00:04:28.672
God, that you would do something miraculous.

00:04:29.472 --> 00:04:30.816
And work and

00:04:30.624 --> 00:04:32.864
Hearts and lives

00:04:34.016 --> 00:04:35.072
Today

00:04:38.304 --> 00:04:39.936
In Jesus' name.

00:04:41.312 --> 00:04:42.560
Amen.

